  "2141130": {
    "name": "Road Kings",
    "steam_appid": 2141130,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141130/extras/a6106dcb1abaa63c97e3e4213284ec06.avif?t=1762969720\" width=616 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">驾驶40吨重型半挂，驰骋美国南部滨海平原。穿梭于繁忙的杰克逊维尔与历史悠久的萨凡纳林荫道之间，统筹接单、挂车与路线规划。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">沉浸式地在《公路英雄》的世界中踏上职业征程：从新手司机起步，面对狡黠对手、暖心伙伴、极端天候与险峻路况，最终建立口碑，成长为业界敬重的自主承运司机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141130/extras/52ef930295a422a90ea76ac993b9098b.webp?t=1762969720\" width=616 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141130/extras/661c79f422b67b09346a1c9a6e99d3d4.avif?t=1762969720\" width=616 height=172 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">体验次时代拟真卡车驾驶。载重、车损、制动、扭矩、轮胎与变速箱……你的卡车你来掌控；融合动态天气变化与复杂路面情况。长途驾驶精心重塑的知名品牌卡车，尽览各个区域的丰富细节，打卡标志性地标，接受不曾预料的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141130/extras/5bc59dc664a79d82d91d17ea632beaee.webp?t=1762969720\" width=616 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141130/extras/5a5953e0df1ec3812b31717fd6b5d6f7.avif?t=1762969720\" width=616 height=172 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">剧变的技术、行业、气候背后，一个无情的大企业正盘踞南部，以盈利为名制造灾难。关键时刻只有你能驰援社区、运送关键物资，证明伸出驰援之手也可扭转乾坤。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141130/extras/10269f31b64ad653d182e4a88e8a5f27.webp?t=1762969720\" width=616 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141130/extras/c38f8d0e31ee91796c1930d0a7c23c88.avif?t=1762969720\" width=616 height=172 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">从一个小雇员成长为自主承运人/经理，书写你自己的《公路英雄》故事。选择你的成功之路：或多多开拓客户，或成为少数企业和忠实调度员的御用王牌。打败竞争对手，在同行和派单公司之间赢得声望，并转化为州际公路上的红利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">还可在异步多人模式下创建或加入公司，角逐全球排行榜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141130/extras/973dcb7ea03cc21d7b0b51cfdb0c41d1.webp?t=1762969720\" width=616 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141130/extras/de767b078e5208b69820ed551035dbc0.avif?t=1762969720\" width=616 height=185 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">驾车纵览美景，一睹佛罗里达州至乔治亚州交界公路实景制作的游戏景色。从幽静小道到知名地标，在拟真渲染的美丽世界中自在探索。遵循路标穿梭州际公路，时刻关注油量、警戒州警、恪守运输规章制度——因为一味走捷径将付出金钱、时间与声誉的三重代价。</p>",
